		At the end of the quarter you will have 4 forums filled with messages and file attachments that document your journey through Capstone. 
		You may want to save this work for posterity. If that's the case, SCUCapstone.com provides an archival service. 
		This service costs $12 semi-annually per team (not per individual!). 
		If you subscribe to it, I will leave your forums in their present state and let you use your General Discussion forum to stay in touch with each other. 
		If you decide not to archive your work, I will clean out the Case I, Case II and Capstone forums for you but leave the General Discussion forum for you to stay in touch - for free. 
		I will also allow you to store 1 copy of your final Case I, Case II and Capstone papers in your General Discussion forum.
		</br></br>
		You subscribe by clicking on the Subscribe button. 
		This will take you to a secure PayPal page where you initiate your subscription with a $12 credit card payment for 6 months coverage. 
		At the end of 6 months, PayPal will automatically extend your subscription another 6 months, bill your credit card, and send you an email notification. 
